---
title: Chinese-Style Chicken Wraps with Cabbage & Mango Slaw
description: We don’t think wraps should ever have a bad rap! These ones are bursting with texture and flavor. You’ll mix together tender pre-cooked chicken, cabbage and carrots, peanuts, and chili mayo and wrap it all up in tortillas. On the side there’s a crunchy slaw with juicy mango pieces. All you’ll really have to work on is your wrapping technique and you’re well on your way to a picture-perfect lunch.
